{"tid":1346776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯公開譴責【白衣人】","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:06:24.000Z","uid":147017,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"53373a60d21e8971f2f6a74416eefaf6ff327144","tid":1346776,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:50:02.000Z","msg":"白衣人=CONDOM<br />\n<br />\n仲當何君堯英雄?"},{"pid":"8f0d92f3774e77f6dd818294bf787319487977f6","tid":1346776,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:52:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、</span></span><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以群眾鬥群眾</span></ins></strong>，內耗消耗民意，<br />\n引起眾多火頭，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>燃起多條戰綫，力圖模糊最初目標</ins></strong></span>，<br />\n大家要諗諗點拆<br />\n<br />\n或者好似另外一啲巴絲講，<br />\n陰謀論諗，可能借無差別攻擊事件自製亂象，繼而自己修補亂象，<br />\n繼而挽回民望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二、</span></span>另外大家可以 brainstorm 下：dress code 以顏色區分是否繼續可行？<br />\n如果著 smart casual 恤衫返工裝，<br />\n人人都係打工仔，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>人人都係 water</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n到時打，打打工仔，打平民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三、</span></span>除 TVB 有免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道外，<br />\nViuTV 同奇妙電視應該要同樣加開免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道，<br />\n本身兩台已有班底，只須加開頻道即可<br />\n甚至可考慮<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全港首創本地 24 小時英語新聞頻道</span></ins></strong><br />\nRTHK 31 亦要加強推廣自身頻道<br />\n<br />\n同溫層講，大家都識得睇其他新聞，<br />\n但須知道好多酒樓、食肆冇嘢好播，咪播 TVB 新聞，<br />\n上年紀一輩只識打開對眼就睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四、</span></span>同樣唔可以忽視就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>境外酒店電視落地</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n大家打開酒店電視，睇香港嘅頻道，只會搵到 TVB，得 TVB 落到地，<br />\n呢方面要大家諗諗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>（外地人士第一觀感）</ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"099d983180528aa9e0912227f3f83892573a63fa","tid":1346776,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"握手.jpg"},{"pid":"b738b0f3f0537a805fa9402657357b3080c16c78","tid":1346776,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"有事咪割蓆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e6040aa101f20e2a4d1b764d223d42539168ec","tid":1346776,"uid":264369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"屌佢話乜 enough is enough<br />\n乘機宣傳佢話唔再批民陣Ｄ伸請<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">家陣有43萬人用腳話 Not enough 呀佢老母</span>"},{"pid":"369d0df9ef4b5c47e09fded9525ec9a9c7c20f95","tid":1346776,"uid":42720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:58:07.000Z","msg":"真係垃圾都有用過佢"},{"pid":"382d2a719fa441b1f32e29b4faeba5cd6192b82d","tid":1346776,"uid":36702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"條數佢幫手開   <br />\n<br />\n班黑社會有咩謂   <br />\n<br />\n佢地最開心係差佬唔拉   仲有錢收"},{"pid":"115458a2a372c6d14bb208f2d5e257481281bf69","tid":1346776,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53373a60d21e8971f2f6a74416eefaf6ff327144","tid":1346776,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:50:02.000Z","msg":"白衣人=CONDOM<br />\n<br />\n仲當何君堯英雄?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"黑社會收錢第一<br />\n<br />\n其他野冇必要講"},{"pid":"86e691847066cdd372dae9dd8e110cf4e19c5f2c","tid":1346776,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"382d2a719fa441b1f32e29b4faeba5cd6192b82d","tid":1346776,"uid":36702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"條數佢幫手開   <br />\n<br />\n班黑社會有咩謂   <br />\n<br />\n佢地最開心係差佬唔拉   仲有錢收"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:28.000Z","msg":"有班廢老,真係當佢英雄<br />\n你睇片握手片"},{"pid":"8833bc322c4d8117e02f3